properties.areaDesc: Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA; Chesapeake Bay from Windmill Point to New Point Comfort VA
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 27 at 3:34AM EST until January 28 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and
waves 3 ft expected.

* WHERE...Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA
and Chesapeake Bay from Windmill Point to New Point Comfort VA.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 10 AM EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 10 AM EST TUESDAY
